problem_data.title: Count Numbers with Unique Digits
problem_data.description: Given an integer n, return the count of all numbers with unique digits, x, where 0 <= x < 10^n.

examples.explanation: The answer should be the total numbers in the range of 0 ≤ x < 100, excluding 11,22,33,44,55,66,77,88,99
